reviews.text: Very good and authentic Hong Kong breakfast. The porridge is very soft. The soy bean also taste good and fresh.
very reasonable price but the taste of everything is so so and they don't have a lot of stuff they listed on The menu.
This congee shop serves tasty congee and Steamed Vermicelli Roll. The preserved egg with minced beef congee (皮蛋碎牛粥) and the steamed vermicelli roll with shrimp (蝦米腸粉) are my favorites.
Value option, lots of choice, good quality. Have to mention, there air conditioning is the best
Four stars for delicious yet inexpensive indigenous foods here. Wanna know what local people eat? Try this tiny shop.
